# Exploration: df

## Rounds
  round 0: 420 isolated cumulative, 33 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 15/16 flags
  15 solo, 0 via combination
  1 additional error-differentiated
  robustness: 15 robust, 0 moderate, 0 fragile

